        "subject": "LU-8728 tests: fix conf-sanity:88 for multiple MDS case",
        "message": "LU-8728 tests: fix conf-sanity:88 for multiple MDS case\n\nstart_mds starts all MDSs. lctl clear_conf fails because\nit expects only one mds combined with mgs started with\nnosvc option. The fix is to force start_mdt to start only\nneeded mds.\n\nSimilarly for combined MDS1 and MGS force stop_mdt to\nstop only needed mds.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial testlist=conf-sanity\nSigned-off-by: Hema Yarramilli <hema.yarramilli@seagate.com>\nSigned-off-by: Arshad Hussain <arshad.hussain@seagate.com>\nChange-Id: Iacc52127b0b93e736430cc13d4c9c852eac8dc2d\nSeagate-bug-id: MRP-2825\nReviewed-by: Vladimir Saveliev <vladimir.saveliev@seagate.com>\nReviewed-by: Ujjwal Lanjewar <ujjwal.lanjewar@seagate.com>\nTested-by: Elena V. Gryaznova <elena.gryaznova@seagate.com>\nReviewed-by: Alexey Leonidovich Lyashkov <alexey.lyashkov@seagate.com>\n"
      },
